{"tid":280400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"私補撚入黎講下你遇過嘅學生/家長有幾癡撚線","createTime":"2017-06-12T05:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T05:16:10.000Z","uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11478d8738579f4e8567019c4f361167f7ea678e","tid":280400,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"我前後補過5個<br />\n其中一個依家F1，補親習全家都參與，父母輪流坐係客廳全程監視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每隔十至二十分鐘就會走埋黎睇下我教成點<br />\n有時仲要加幾句阻撚住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒你地咁得閒平時就自己教翻啦<br />\n終於有一次佢父母都唔係屋企<br />\n好啦諗住今堂可以靜靜地<br />\n屌你老味佢阿婆係間房到行出嚟<br />\n仲同我講今堂要做邊啲啊邊啲又係聽日功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住唔使講又係全堂坐係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個下真係唔撚識俾反應，點撚解可以補習補到阿婆都要參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時下社會究竟發生乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efae9ea81887eb139d96d15b52d322d6cfff681","tid":280400,"uid":9092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"樓主year幾"},{"pid":"730795e71f0317c7ee1a771a2af0427e3030b6a6","tid":280400,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"咪出聲講囉<br />\n你坐係到影響到我教 影響到小朋友學"},{"pid":"f3ff65e54bf07275490916fb8f1a0a2e70f65b9a","tid":280400,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf3c2762e17683dfdaa05087de2be82fcb2ee0e6","tid":280400,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主year幾</blockquote><br />\n2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}